</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Recorder (judge)</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p>A <b>Recorder</b> is a judicial officer in England and Wales and some other common law jurisdictions.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
<div id="toctitle">
