<li id="cite_note-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">M.G. Easton. "<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/easton/ebd2.html?term=Recorder">Recorder</a>." <i>Easton's Bible Dictionary</i>. Grand Rapids, MI: Christian Classics Ethereal Library, 1897.</span></li>
